divs: Sighting DetailsI was helping my neighbor move...I noticed a small cloud it was tiny and it was sitting in the sunset...I got my camera and took pictures of it (my grandaughter had sent me a pic of a lone cloud and I was wanting to send one back) so without hesitation I got my camera and began zooming in and looking at taking a good pic of what I think is a cloud...I did not look at my pictures I took I put away my camera and went about helping my neighbor...then I look up and there is this big streek coming from right where I saw the cloud or what I think is a cloud...I run and get my camera ...this cloud was not moving at all or it was moving twards me I don't know...but I ran got my camera and did the same zooming in and out taking as many pictures as I liked...and did not look at them until later that evening...our mouths dropped open as we looked at what I photgraphed...you have a look...this is not a contrail in my openion :D
